<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf63c21b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s12164"><num value="12164">§ 12164.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Not later than 1 year after <date date="1990-07-26">July 26, 1990</date>, the Secretary of Transportation shall issue regulations, in an accessible format, necessary for carrying out this subpart.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbf63c21c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/336/tII/s244">Pub. L. 101–336, title II, § 244</ref>, <date date="1990-07-26">July 26, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/352">104 Stat. 352</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbf63c21d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idbf63c21e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idbf63c21f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1990-07-26">July 26, 1990</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/101/336/s246/b">section 246(b) of Pub. L. 101–336</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s12161">section 12161 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
